tweet: JUULing is highly addictive, dangerous, and fueling an epidemic among our children. I refuse to allow another generation of young people to become addicted to nicotine. That’s why I am investigating JUUL’s business practices. 3/3

tweet: From 2017 to 2018, the number of high schoolers self-reporting that they smoked an e-cig in the past 30 days skyrocketed by 78% to over 3m teenagers! The vast majority smoke JUULs, which dominates the market due to its social marketing, fruit flavors, & slick USB-like design. 2/3

name: Josh Stein
tweet: If you weren’t concerned about JUUL yesterday, you should be today. The CDC released a youth survey which showed the single greatest year over year increase in teenager use of any product in the 44 year history of the survey. 1/3
